  "body": "We have been trying to setup geth on our AWS infrastructure for over a month now, but it still has not synced.\r\n\r\nUseful information:\r\n- Geth fast mode\r\n- > eth.syncing\r\n{\r\n  currentBlock: 10969281,\r\n  highestBlock: 10969437,\r\n  knownStates: 851958910,\r\n  pulledStates: 851958909,\r\n  startingBlock: 10968794\r\n}\r\n- the currentBlock never catches up with the highestBlock\r\n- on AWS weâ€™re using a t2.large to sync with EFS (instance is on a VPC with NAT)\r\n\r\ngeth CLI opts:  --datadir /mnt/geth --cache=55000",
